cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is about improving the efficiency of salient object detection models, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves designing a new convolutional module and a dynamic weight decay scheme, which are techniques that can be applied to various neural network architectures and optimization algorithms, respectively. Therefore, this paper could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on salient object detection benchmarks, which is a task related to multimedia (cs.MM).
